{
  "stem": "13063.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the major of-- of the SS who-- who [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] oversaw this action.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he stood at-- Thiele stood at attention.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is the group that I am requesting that should be apportioned to our workplace.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he looked at-- looked at us, this SS major, he said, but if you don't work, you are-- you are going to hear from me if you don't work diligently.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he left us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What did he look like?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very handsome, very handsome-looking man, with-- with epaulets and-- you know how those German SS people looked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Haase, he was-- he was extremely dignified-looking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I understood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, I already understood some German because I-- I was exposed to German for years now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this is how I was saved on October 22, 1942.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother and sister went to Belzec to be killed because they were Jews-- because they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the only reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remained in the ghetto [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with my father and with some-- with the remainder of the Jews who somehow saved themselves also through-- through work, or some German took them under their so-called fatherly wings.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The minority of Jews remained, because the majority was really transported.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The ghetto was shrunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was cut in half and shrunk at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, in Sonderdienst, all the time in Sonderdienst.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Afterwards, about one month or two months after the-- after-- in October-- after October 22-- I think it was either November or December-- my father and-- my father got some pull, you know, in-- in the ghetto, and he was engaged by Madritsch.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
